{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f703f8cf03","title":"在中共中央群众接待站传讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0604393cbd","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":10,"articleId":"f703f8cf03"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cd0b95746f","type":"paragraph","text":"生的文化大革命行动看来，我不相信有正民主，正克思主义，而是站在资产阶级方面反对无产阶级文化大革命。团中央不仅不支持青年学生运动，反而压学生运动，我看该处理。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"f96fb02372","type":"paragraph","text":"炮打司合部","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"96262de54e","type":"paragraph","text":"我的一张大字报","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"498b8d6307","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月五日）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"abe65ee062","type":"paragraph","text":"全国第一张马列主义的大字报和《人民日报》评论员的评论，写得何等好呵！腊同志们重读一通这张大字报和这个评论。可是在五十多天里，从中央到地方的某些领导同志，却反其道而行之，站在反动的资产阶级立场上，实行资产阶级专政，将无产阶级轰轰烈烈的文化大革命运动打下去，倒是非，混潘黑白，围剩革命派，压制不同意见，实行白色恐饰，自以为得意，长资产阶级的威风，灭无产阶级的志气，又何其毒也！联系到一九六二年的右倾和一九六四年的形“左”而实右的错澳倾向，自不是可以发人深醒的吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"6a63073148","type":"paragraph","text":"毛东在修改《欢呼北大的一张大字报》","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"156d264237","type":"paragraph","text":"一文时加的一段器","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"c3a77f5f42","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月五日）","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"f686906a98","type":"paragraph","text":"危害革命的错识领导，不应当无条件接受，而应当坚决抵制。在这次文化大革命中，广大革命师生及革命干部对于错误的领导，就广泛地进行过抵制","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"74c8303062","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央基众接待站的斋","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"c74c36ea37","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月十日）你们要关心国家大事，要把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底！","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"d0456cf7c7","type":"paragraph","text":"对檬黄田大字报的批示","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"cde34be307","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六六年八月）印发全会（指十一中全会）各同志。将杨寅田大字报题目用特号字，全文用老五号刊出。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"},{"id":"20a0f26cc0","type":"paragraph","text":"·267","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03"}],"page":{"id":"9bab468cef","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f703f8cf03","start":280,"end":280}}}},"__N_SSG":true}